{"tid":1560161,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【1時34分更新：傳4點記招講釋放農地】","createTime":"2019-09-11T05:57:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T14:27:25.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"6ca301641b3a5e94b72287671e3e2bb968ee68fa","tid":1560161,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T05:57:23.000Z","msg":"【1時34分更新：傳4點記招講釋放農地】<br />\n<br />\n今早11時34分左右，網上引述《南華早報》消息指出，港府將於今日下午4時前，回應示威者的另一訴求。其後有消息指，港府將於4點收市後會有記者會講釋放農地》。<br />\n<br />\n另外，《香港經濟日報》引述消息指，民建聯近日向特首林鄭月娥力推《收回土地條例》，收回農地建公營房屋，林鄭對此不再抗拒。<br />\n<br />\n本地地產股午後持續造好，新世界（017）、新地（016）、長實（1113）、恒地（012）升逾3%，信置（083）亦升逾2%。<br />\n<br />\n翻查年報，截至2018年底，恒地持有4560萬平方呎農地，為本港擁有最多新界農地的發展商。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tastymoneyhk/photos/a.371518376517808/971984309804542/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftastymoneyhk%2Fphotos%2Fa.371518376517808%2F971984309804542%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWQPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=e7f88a84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tastymoneyhk/photos/a.371518376517808/971984309804542/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"349fbc8baefc3f6bb791a1fa3eb397f6e3c7a833","tid":1560161,"uid":248404,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T05:59:35.000Z","msg":"釋放農地其實咪姐係比錢鄉黑同發展商"},{"pid":"c350c2a8bd1632fc72bbff7c3941d37482d56c13","tid":1560161,"uid":65738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:03:21.000Z","msg":"關係法GO AHEAD, 嚇死咪撚縮"},{"pid":"7445e40176d3d0671993cd08126c03572900f91a","tid":1560161,"uid":248404,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:03:25.000Z","msg":"咁大件事唔講？西瓜達人打完記者，而家政府仲超高價收佢塊地呀。"},{"pid":"3c915dd4dad0844a30c0f6c27e47cf0958e926c1","tid":1560161,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:04:10.000Z","msg":"丁權？"},{"pid":"399cbeaef39ec92e9dedb0aa55ff7099265b9cb1","tid":156